Atlantic Ocean storms 2005

Source: R/data.R
atlStorms2005.Rd

Atlantic Ocean storms 2005

Format

sp::SpatialLinesDataFrame

Details

This dataset contains storm tracks for selected storms in the Atlantic Ocean basin for the year 2005
